➜【星连文学社】湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：窗 帘
http://www.sohu.com/a/413390002_100115135	34218
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200816/3e9ce5a3b60b415eaf0453a99b8fe353.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>窗 帘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打开与世间对望的眼睛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看芸芸众生朝露待日晞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去日苦多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万象从流草木春秋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">熟悉或陌生交织着逝情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>目光止于窗帘外光的花影</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>止于幻梦，幽冥里不去想雨水风声</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>尘喧翻不过思绪城墙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可供我闭目清静</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>禅光在心，烘热潮湿光阴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">写于2020年8月15日晚九点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200816/b248b891f96f4c23985f792a0963bde7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
