<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>微诗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一缕月光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">潜入荷池</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纹一圈一圈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直达彼岸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">缝合了夜的黑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风穿梭于竹林</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那弯弯的月刚要回眸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却又起程</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200816/a5a9dc1b7e3b4ae694b91079ad23c3d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
